run in Idea with following VM options

--module-path ${PATH_TO_FX} --add-modules=javafx.controls,javafx.fxml
(add PATH_TO_FX in Idea path variables)

or

run just in Idea with following VM options (change to actual path javafx-sdk: ...\Plasmirror\javafx-sdk\javafx-sdk-11.0.2\lib)
Windows:
--module-path C:\Users\Decorus\IdeaProjects\Plasmirror\javafx-sdk-win\javafx-sdk-11.0.2\lib --add-modules=javafx.controls,javafx.fxml

Mac:
--module-path C:\Users\Decorus\IdeaProjects\Plasmirror\javafx-sdk-mac\javafx-sdk-11.0.2\lib --add-modules=javafx.controls,javafx.fxml

